highlights.text: “Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 154 days straight.
“Shiny” by Easykid and Dysbit is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #48.
EsDeeKid has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Phantom” is the highest at #20.
“Wish (feat. Trippie Redd) - Trippie Mix” by Diplo and Trippie Redd is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 26 spots at #68.
